Autoposting Script License

This license grants the right to use this script in your own projects,
as well as modify and customize it for personal use. 
However, using the script to present it as your own development 
or selling the script without the author's knowledge and consent is strictly prohibited.

The author retains all rights to the source code 
and may make changes to the usage terms at any time.

Use of the script for commercial purposes is permitted 
only with the author's written permission. 
